Class Overview

A MenuItem that represents a single item in the menu. Use MenuItem.Builder to build a MenuItem.

MenuItem can be customized with title, subtitle, and icon (left and right). A MenuItem can be one of the following three (3) types:

  • Submenu. Allows the user to go one level deeper into the submenu.
  • Checkbox. Allows the user to toggle the checkbox. The drawer does not close automatically when the user taps the checkbox item.
  • Normal menu item. The item can be customized with title, subtitle and left and right icons.
